{"tid":598264,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人屋企有毒撚家庭成員","createTime":"2018-03-19T11:05:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T12:19:40.000Z","uid":168142,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"152d64100f1292e10d7b78949806a4e61ee09624","tid":598264,"uid":168142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:05:37.000Z","msg":"屋企有件毒撚真係好難頂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n長期一陣酸臭味環繞住個人<br />\n啲油份又唔知點解可以比一般人旺盛咁多<br />\n就算佢自己摺埋做自己事都好<br />\n個衛生情況都好影響身邊嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又成日將啲打完飛機嘅紙巾四圍擺(飯枱，衣櫥，雪櫥)<br />\n明明有垃圾筒<br />\n可以夜晚食食下飯到一半走左去打飛機<br />\n打完再出黎繼續食都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟係咩事令香港依個地方咁多毒撚存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71d4e89b8505da21e8ea4e8e77b60510603df1e","tid":598264,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:07:39.000Z","msg":"原來打飛機真係有大宗師"},{"pid":"847999d13196c63a6fc521ba71351628457beee1","tid":598264,"uid":146299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:07:48.000Z","msg":"你細佬定阿爸"},{"pid":"3815abc66a582567bfb8185f6c8972eb4f633e04","tid":598264,"uid":167359,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:08:23.000Z","msg":"夜晚食食下飯都有性慾⋯ 伯母裸體圍裙？"},{"pid":"0cfd5b8bfb568737145083d19f08bc5aeb5debca","tid":598264,"uid":43231,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:09:20.000Z","msg":"人哋就飽暖思淫慾<br />\n佢就飽暖中淫慾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"facbb5a5e22750d05063ede0513f628da4414398","tid":598264,"uid":15220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T11:09:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇咁癲呀，含住啖飯飯飛機"},{"pid":"10be0598e999f7fb4361394b5d6859858ba7ee84","tid":598264,"